  "remarks": "Subordinate of the DTRSC within MODAFL. This includes research groups\npreviously falling under the Physics Research Center (PHRC). IAEA inspectors have not\nbeen allowed to interview staff or see documents under the control of this organization\nto resolve the outstanding issue of the possible military dimension to Iran's nuclear\nprogramme. [Old Reference # E.29.I.9]",
